cloud·scape    ( P )  Pronunciation Key  (kloudskp)
n. 
A work of art representing a view of clouds: an Impressionist painting that is a vast cloudscape of buoyant, floating forms. 
A photograph showing a view of clouds, such as those surrounding a planet. 
 

